Overview:

The system allows an Android device to control a Kobuki mobile robot through USB communication while supporting movement commands, audio interaction, and experimental computer vision features.

Features:

Android application for robot control
Stable USB communication with Kobuki robot
Manual movement controls (forward, backward, rotate, stop)
Basic audio interaction
Experimental computer vision
Modular system integration

Technologies:
Android Studio
Java / Kotlin
OpenCV
Kobuki Base Controller
GitHub
